                              углублении.</seg>
                           <seg xml:lang="en"><rs type="execution" ref="execution.xml#scalpro"/> On the front, below the cornice, within a wide (5 x 18cm) inset
                              rectangle.</seg>
                        </layout>
                     </layoutDesc>
